text: Anticipated #vaccine supply for 65+ in #Japan seems to increase rapidly starting in May, but I’ve seen no discussion of planned/anticipated #vaccination rates/capacity. Completing 2 doses to 30 (of 36) mill 65+ between May 1 and, say, July 15 requires 400-450K vax/day.   #COVID19 https://t.co/HSIdNgaSoM
